  <scopecontent id="aspace_3fb04246e5c8af168c645e5f81d05f8c">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>The collection includes a field journal, two fair-copy journals, an annotated 1844 map of Iceland, several proof sections of Shepherd's The North-West Peninsula of Iceland (1867) and a copy of the published book. It also includes correspondence and newspaper clippings.</p>  </scopecontent>
